<i>In Naniwa Bay</i>

712
00:49:16,787 --> 00:49:18,747
<i>Behold how the flower blooms</i>

713
00:49:18,830 --> 00:49:20,916
<i>After winter's sleep</i>

714
00:49:20,999 --> 00:49:22,209
Let's go, Umezono!

715
00:49:22,876 --> 00:49:23,752
Right!

